=== apt-sync Benchmarks ===

==== Jaunty ====

Below benchmarks are shown for an upgrade from vanilla Jaunty to the latest patch-set using apt-sync (see also <nowiki>[[AptSyncInKarmicSpec-KarmicBenchmark|Karmic upgrade benchmarks]]</nowiki>). The overall statistics are:

* 249 aptsync files created, with a total size of 2.9MB.
* Total update size is 165.6MB, of which 77.9MB were downloaded (total saving of 53%).
* Out of aptsyncable* files: 116.6MB of which 28.9MB downloaded (total saving of 75%).
* Out of non-aptsyncable* files: 49.0MB of which 49.0MB downloaded (total saving of 0%).

Full log available <nowiki>[[AptSyncInKarmicSpec-Jaunty|here]]</nowiki>.

* For a package to be "aptsyncable", there must be a previous version installed on the system and the compression format must be gzip (currently lzma and bzip2 are not supported).
